#H bit | arpStat | Description
#H =============================================================================
     0 | 0x01    | ARP detected
#W   1 | 0x02    | MAC/IP list truncated... increase MAX_IP
     2 | 0x04    | -
     3 | 0x08    | Gratuitous ARP (sender IP same as target IP)
     4 | 0x10    | -
     5 | 0x20    | -
     6 | 0x40    | -
#W   7 | 0x80    | ARP spoofing (same IP assigned to multiple MAC)
